  "title": "Business Manager (Recruitment)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<p>* Reporting to Managing Director/CEO based in Singapore</p>\n<p>* ⁠Direct accelerated career path to be Practice Leader - Associated Director </p>\n<p>* ⁠Starting as an individual contributor to forming your own Cluster with the goal of growing your team</p>\n<p>* ⁠Focusing on one industry</p>\n<p>* ⁠Executing 360-degree recruitment cycle of Business Development and Recruitment</p>\n<p>* ⁠Identifying business opportunities through customer prospecting and sales pitching</p>\n<p>* ⁠Handling end-to-end recruitment process</p>\n<p>* ⁠Maintaining relationship with clients and candidates</p>\n<p>* ⁠Optimizing your cluster’s profitability through achieving target in business development and recruitment</p>\n<p>* ⁠Responsible for the profit and loss (P&amp;L) scheme of your cluster</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<p>* Experiences in 360-degree recruitment cycle</p>\n<p>* ⁠Extensive knowledge and skill in business development or B2B sales</p>\n<p>* ⁠Proven record in business development and recruitment</p>\n<p>* ⁠Target driven and passionate to grow</p>\n<p>* ⁠Able to work independently in a dynamic and fast-paced environment</p>",
