    "description": "<p>Tech Grid Asia is your trusted career partner in the ASEAN region, with roots in Singapore and a growing presence in Thailand and Indonesia. We specialize in helping jobseekers like you find meaningful roles with leading employers across industries.<br>\n<br>\nWhether you're looking for opportunities in tech or non-tech roles, permanent positions or contract work, we’re here to support you every step of the way. Our experienced recruiters work closely with top companies to match the right talent with the right opportunities—and that could be you.<br>\n<br>\nAt Tech Grid Asia, we believe that a job should be more than just work. That’s why we take the time to understand your skills, aspirations, and what truly matters to you. Our goal is to connect you with roles where you can grow, thrive, and build a fulfilling career.<br>\n<br>\nLet us help you take the next step. Explore new possibilities with Tech Grid Asia—your future starts here.</p>",
